▪️2016 MX champion

node.text:
Since I haven’t seen the track yet, I hit up the local @chaseelliott9 for some Atlanta Speedway advice. We’re gonna keep it low and consistent. Rights don’t matter! 🏁

@ktmusa @redbull @teamhendrick @supercrosslive @nascar

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Cooper Webb in Pala Raceway with @alpinestars, and @alpinestarsmx. May be an image of boots.

node.text:
13 U.S. 🇺🇸 service members will be riding with me tomorrow — 10 of those from nearby Camp Pendleton. I'm incredibly thankful for our heroes who have fought and continue to fight for our great nation and I’ll never forget their sacrifice 🙏🏼

@alpinestars @alpinestarsmx
